{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-2-chapter-level-2-tsx","path":"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/background-information/impact/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"e78d2f1a-689e-52ef-aeba-55972f596dd9","slug":"impact","fullItemName":"Impact","depth":2,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 117022fe-a05a-47b9-8477-ea39d95087bd --><h2>What is the impact of bedwetting?</h2><!-- end field 117022fe-a05a-47b9-8477-ea39d95087bd -->","summary":"","htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 18fb661f-7fc6-4531-987d-34ce4cf441e4 --><!-- begin field eb37fffb-ca9a-496d-98a1-7ae233719556 --><ul><li><strong>Bedwetting can have a deep impact on the child or young person's emotional and social wellbeing as well as their behaviour </strong>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/references/\">National Clinical Guideline Centre, 2010</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/references/\">EAU, 2019</a>]<strong>. </strong><ul><li>Children and young people with bedwetting may [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/references/\">National Clinical Guideline Centre, 2010</a>]:<ul><li>Feel guilt, shame, humiliation, victimization, or loss of self-esteem. They may also have a feeling of helplessness, or a lack of hope and optimism. In addition, they may feel that they are different from other children.</li><li>Avoid social activities, such as sleepovers or school trips.</li><li>Have higher than average levels of oppositional behaviour and conduct problems [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/references/\">Joinson et al, 2007</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/references/\">BMJ, 2019</a>].</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><strong>Bedwetting can be stressful for the parents or carers of the child or young person </strong>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/references/\">EAU, 2019</a>]<strong>.</strong><ul><li>The cost of caring for a child or young person with bedwetting can be considerable (for example the cost of extra laundry, extra bed sheets, mattress replacement, pull ups), which can have a significant effect on family finances.</li><li>There is a risk that a minority of parents/carers may punish the child or young person for wetting the bed (including physical punishment) [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bedwetting-enuresis/references/\">Sapi, 2009</a>].</li></ul></li></ul><p> </p><!-- end field eb37fffb-ca9a-496d-98a1-7ae233719556 --><!-- end item 18fb661f-7fc6-4531-987d-34ce4cf441e4 -->","topic":{"id":"494d35c8-2f43-5deb-bf3b-a6b8fe526ea5","topicId":"ce6704cc-49b8-49dd-8017-46b17a9f54dc","topicName":"Bedwetting (enuresis)","slug":"bedwetting-enuresis","lastRevised":"Last revised in March 2020","chapters":[{"id":"e2f46040-a7ac-5c61-8537-6a4d74c4b74d","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"28213f9e-2495-5a2c-987f-a266a76263cc","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"6f8d63a7-374f-5b82-b946-89121a397f09","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"36341e41-edc3-52d1-b532-c04d123aed4f","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"607f4074-ebbe-5809-9dd3-ba440f495c9e","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"5b8b9c48-6d10-5875-8b99-310381a0345e","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"c173ebac-5a35-5f86-8886-c812c29d9dda","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"610216bd-181e-57fc-81fe-e4b91ba2dd06","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"3605b61c-296c-52ea-ba7d-89032c76153a","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit crit